on hookers or private planes.

118
00:04:15,572 --> 00:04:17,138
It's a latte.

119
00:04:17,207 --> 00:04:19,319
I'm gonna get you one
of those milk-frothy things.

120
00:04:19,343 --> 00:04:21,676
I'm gonna teach you how
to make your own latte.

121
00:04:21,745 --> 00:04:23,862
Will you do it in that swimsuit?

122
