then what did you say?

224
00:08:11,391 --> 00:08:12,802
"Thank you."

225
00:08:12,826 --> 00:08:14,303
Cristina... No,
no, really, really,

226
00:08:14,327 --> 00:08:15,943
it's just a nomination.

227
00:08:16,012 --> 00:08:19,080
I'm happy about it, but
I've got a ton of work to do.

228
00:08:19,149 --> 00:08:20,531
I want to focus on that.

229
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:23,768
I really don't want to
make a big deal out of it.

230
00:08:23,837 --> 00:08:25,782
Hey, hey. Let's
go this way. Yeah.

231
00:08:25,806 --> 00:08:27,055
You know, get some breakfast?

232
00:08:27,123 --> 00:08:28,639
