236
00:08:43,606 --> 00:08:45,440
Meredith's.

237
00:08:45,508 --> 00:08:47,175
Congratulations, Yang.

238
00:09:03,109 --> 00:09:07,378
Innovation.
Imagination. Excellence.

239
00:09:07,447 --> 00:09:11,082
