and has applications

245
00:09:21,928 --> 00:09:23,405
for the work that he
and Dr. Torres are doing.

246
00:09:23,429 --> 00:09:24,696
Torres! Me!

247
00:09:24,764 --> 00:09:27,231
Hey, Dr. Grey is
about to do the first

248
00:09:27,300 --> 00:09:31,002
