kidney transplant in the state

249
00:09:31,071 --> 00:09:32,764
since the new law went
into effect in November.

250
00:09:32,788 --> 00:09:33,933
That's history in
the making. It's mine.

251
00:09:33,957 --> 00:09:35,640
And Dr. Bailey's looking for

252
00:09:35,709 --> 00:09:38,192
